text: Al-Gharafa S.C. is a professional football club which plays in Qatar. It is based in Doha, Qatar. It plays in the Qatar Star League. It is one of the most successful in the history of Qatar football, winning many trophies. Al-Gharafa has won sixteen titles, seven QSL League, six Prince Cups, two Crown Pirnce Cups and one Arab league Cup. == Name == * 1979-2004 Al-Ittihad Doha * 2004-present Al-Gharafa S.C.
